    • Method Detail

      • actionCustDelete

        public void actionCustDelete​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
        Action event for delete button on customer screen. If no customer is selected, an error message will be generated and if a valid customer is selected and has no attached appointments, a warning message to confirm removal will be generated and once OK is selected - the customer will be deleted from the database and the list of customers refreshed in the tableview. If appointments are found for a customer - an alert will be generated to confirm both removal of the associated appointments and customer.
        Parameters:
        actionEvent - event for when delete button on customer screen is pressed
